com.ebay.sdk.attributes.model
Interface ICategoryCSProvider

All Known Implementing Classes:
CategoryCSDownloader
public interface ICategoryCSProvider

Supplies categoryId to CSId convertion service for IAttributesMaster. It provides mapping between categoryID and CSId.
